HEADWORD: googly
<hw>googly</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Cricket)</fld> <def>a cricket ball
bowled as if to break one way that actually breaks in the opposite
way.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> wrong 'un, bosie, bosie ball.</syn>⟦br⟧
